{"_id":"nhsdeathguard001","name":"Spirit Shroud (Concealed in Horde)","type":"effect","img":"icons/magic/unholy/silhouette-robe-evil-power.webp","system":{"slug":"spirit-shroud-concealed","description":{"value":"<p>You are sharing a space with a Deathguard necrologist's horde. The press of twisted limbs and swirling ectoplasm hides you from view, making you @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.DmAIPqOBomZ7H95W]{Concealed} to all creatures.</p><p><em>Applied automatically by the Necrologist Horde Sync module when an ally shares the horde's space. Removed automatically when the ally leaves.</em></p>"},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":1},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":null},"tokenIcon":{"show":true},"badge":null,"context":null,"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"unidentified":false,"rules":[{"key":"GrantItem","uuid":"Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.DmAIPqOBomZ7H95W","onDeleteActions":{"granter":"restrict"}}]},"flags":{"necrologist-horde-sync":{"bundled":true}}}
{"_id":"nhsspirithorde01","name":"Spirit Horde","type":"effect","img":"icons/magic/death/undead-ghost-scream-teal.webp","system":{"slug":"spirit-horde","description":{"value":"<p>This horde is composed of spirits rather than zombies. While active, the horde gains the incorporeal trait, the standard incorporeal IWR, and its Mobbing Assault deals void damage.</p><p><em>Granted automatically by Necrologist Horde Sync when the summoner has the Ghost Song feat and toggles Spirit Horde on. Removed when toggled off.</em></p>"},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":1},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":null},"tokenIcon":{"show":true},"badge":null,"context":null,"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"unidentified":false,"rules":[{"key":"ActorTraits","add":["incorporeal"]},{"key":"Immunity","exceptions":[],"type":["precision","disease","paralyzed","poison"]},{"key":"Resistance","type":["physical"],"value":5,"exceptions":["force","ghost-touch"]},{"key":"DamageAlteration","mode":"override","property":"damage-type","value":"void","predicate":[{"or":["item:slug:mobbing-assault","item:name:Mobbing Assault"]}],"selectors":["mobbing-assault"]}]},"flags":{"necrologist-horde-sync":{"bundled":true}}}
{"_id":"nhsspirithordet1","name":"Spirit Horde Toggle","type":"effect","img":"icons/magic/death/undead-ghost-scream-teal.webp","system":{"slug":"spirit-horde-toggle","description":{"value":"<p>Toggle this on when you Raise your Horde to make it a spirit horde (incorporeal, Mobbing Assault deals void damage).</p><p><em>Automatic — granted by Necrologist Horde Sync when you take the Ghost Song feat. Toggling this grants/removes the Spirit Horde effect on your linked horde(s).</em></p>"},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":1},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":null},"tokenIcon":{"show":false},"badge":null,"context":null,"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"unidentified":false,"rules":[{"key":"RollOption","option":"spirit-horde","toggleable":true,"value":false}]},"flags":{"necrologist-horde-sync":{"bundled":true}}}
